{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"5514","heading":"Acquisition accountability on the missile defense system","label":"5514 Acquisition accountability on the missile defense system","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s5514","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptVI/sptA/ch551/schII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs5514","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in Text, referred to in subsec. (a)(1)(A), was repealed by , , . See .Section 223 of this titlePub. L. 118–159, div. A, title XVI, § 1649(b)(1)138 Stat. 2199section 5511 of this titleDec. 23, 2024","Prior ProvisionsProvisions similar to those in this section were contained in prior to repeal by , , .section 225 of this titlePub. L. 118–159, div. A, title XVI, § 1649(b)(1)138 Stat. 2199Dec. 23, 2024","Amendments2025—Subsec. (b)(2)(C)(ii). substituted “reviewed” for “approved”.Pub. L. 119–60","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Improvement to Operations and Sustainment Cost Estimates, , , provided that:Pub. L. 113–66, div. A, title II, § 231(a)127 Stat. 710Dec. 26, 2013“In preparing the acquisition accountability reports on the ballistic missile defense system required by [former] , United States Code, the Director of the Missile Defense Agency shall improve the quality of cost estimates relating to operations and sustainment that are included in such reports under subsection (b)(3)(A) of such section, including with respect to the confidence levels of such cost estimates.”section 225 of title 10"],"amendments":["References in Text, referred to in subsec. (a)(1)(A), was repealed by , , . See .Section 223 of this titlePub. L. 118–159, div. A, title XVI, § 1649(b)(1)138 Stat. 2199section 5511 of this titleDec. 23, 2024","Prior ProvisionsProvisions similar to those in this section were contained in prior to repeal by , , .section 225 of this titlePub. L. 118–159, div. A, title XVI, § 1649(b)(1)138 Stat. 2199Dec. 23, 2024","A